Abstract = {{Recent evidence points to an overlap in the neural systems processing
   pain and social distress. In this functional MRI study we focus on the
   possible interplay between the processing of a psychosocial stressor and
   somatic pain within pain responsive brain regions, the latter being
   identified in an independent localizer experiment. A paradigm based on
