Abstract = {{This functional magnetic resonance imaging study examined medial
   prefrontal cortex (mPFC) activity as young and older participants rated
   an unknown young and older person, and themselves, on personality
   characteristics. For both young and older participants, there was
   greater activation in ventral mPFC (anterior cingulate) when they made
