   target age and participant age, there was greater activity in a more
   anterior region of ventral mPFC (largely medial frontal gyrus, anterior
   cingulate) when participants rated others than when they rated
   themselves. We discuss potential interpretations of these findings in
   the context of previous results suggesting functional specificity of
